    "name": "迪姆雷斯",
    "steam_appid": 2402680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迪姆雷斯地底有什么正在蠢蠢欲动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场本应赐予力量的仪式意外失控，你和数位陌生人因此获得了不死之身，从此卷入一段命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在饱受战火摧残的Mirkea大地，古老的废墟低声诉说着被遗忘的魔法，原本分裂的族群正奋力团结起来，决心对抗即将到来的腐化与黑暗。那位强大的法师让你获得了全新的生命——而未来的走向，将由你与伙伴们共同决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以独自踏上冒险，也可以与最多 8 名玩家并肩作战。在荒野中建立属于你的避难所，结识同伴，彼此建立信任与羁绊，甚至收获一段浪漫爱情。加入这场原本不应属于你的战争，迎向仍未书写的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/b976a9d68520a0f7f9584ceb086a7a7d.avif?t=1771381010\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras_big/b976a9d68520a0f7f9584ceb086a7a7d.avif?t=1771381010 width=800 height=33 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/bd707ca3e55355f278f4a12c2b874603.poster.avif?t=1771381010\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/bd707ca3e55355f278f4a12c2b874603.webm?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/bd707ca3e55355f278f4a12c2b874603.mp4?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在濒临崩溃的世界中醒来。一次失败的仪式赋予你不死之身，也将你卷入深藏于 迪姆雷斯地底的古老黑暗之中。揭开被遗忘的秘密，召集盟友，你的选择将改变 Mirkea以及你自己的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/7ed18d1e3ecd5ca0828c5bed52d9b999.avif?t=1771381010\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras_big/7ed18d1e3ecd5ca0828c5bed52d9b999.avif?t=1771381010 width=800 height=33 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/ec538e1c659f85b4654cb3b365e829ce.poster.avif?t=1771381010\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/ec538e1c659f85b4654cb3b365e829ce.webm?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/ec538e1c659f85b4654cb3b365e829ce.mp4?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过灵活的技能树构建角色，结合各族天赋与职业能力，自由定义你的成长之路。你可以化身精灵操控魔法，也可以成为冲锋陷阵的牛头战士，或是开辟一条属于自己的全新道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/a868ff0b270685210a8dd2c8cedb41ab.avif?t=1771381010\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras_big/a868ff0b270685210a8dd2c8cedb41ab.avif?t=1771381010 width=800 height=33 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/90c9d780aab9710f02060047879d7cc1.poster.avif?t=1771381010\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/90c9d780aab9710f02060047879d7cc1.webm?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/90c9d780aab9710f02060047879d7cc1.mp4?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌控真实而策略丰富的元素战斗，释放 300 多种法术，组合元素打出毁灭性效果。随着战斗经验与等级的提升，你的技能树也将不断成长。这里没有随机战斗，胜利永远属于智勇双全的冒险者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/b2a9773a5b5c630196bb5f4b35732e1a.avif?t=1771381010\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras_big/b2a9773a5b5c630196bb5f4b35732e1a.avif?t=1771381010 width=800 height=33 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/1e072c037ae50d590599b4dbed29fe70.poster.avif?t=1771381010\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/1e072c037ae50d590599b4dbed29fe70.webm?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/1e072c037ae50d590599b4dbed29fe70.mp4?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在荒野中开辟你的家园，扩建并装饰据点，与性格迥异的NPC盟友共同度过温馨惬意的时光。新朋友加入带来的也许不止是新的冒险篇章，这里甚至可能上演一段浪漫爱情故事。你的据点将成为黑暗时代中的一束希望之光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/b674ce66c847ce9d3a28bb7d4677b08a.avif?t=1771381010\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras_big/b674ce66c847ce9d3a28bb7d4677b08a.avif?t=1771381010 width=800 height=33 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/0d0a2777271b6fd4a2beb941e13a9175.poster.avif?t=1771381010\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/0d0a2777271b6fd4a2beb941e13a9175.webm?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/0d0a2777271b6fd4a2beb941e13a9175.mp4?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这片美丽无垠的像素风开放世界中，穿越森林、遗迹与失落之地，感受每一次天气变化与季节更替。用你的行为来将影响这片大地，探寻那些埋藏于岩石缝隙与树木枝芽之间关于生命与希望的魔法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/1a9174e98186dd4d3c4e8674ec1ea7e6.avif?t=1771381010\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras_big/1a9174e98186dd4d3c4e8674ec1ea7e6.avif?t=1771381010 width=800 height=33 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/e8cd4ac11f3922a21536dc13caa75032.poster.avif?t=1771381010\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/e8cd4ac11f3922a21536dc13caa75032.webm?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/e8cd4ac11f3922a21536dc13caa75032.mp4?t=1771381010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏支持最多 8 名玩家共同游玩。你可以组建一支冒险小队，齐心协力对抗邪恶；也可以与朋友四处游玩探索，一起建设你们的小小据点。无论独自踏上征程还是与朋友同行，你都能找到属于自己的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras/084b5b5adf9ca43aca3fa1788a529d58.avif?t=1771381010\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402680/extras_big/084b5b5adf9ca43aca3fa1788a529d58.avif?t=1771381010 width=800 height=33 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《迪姆雷斯》目前正在积极开发中，预计将于 2025年8月开启新一轮游戏测试，并在 2026年秋季正式推出抢先体验版本。现在就将我们加入愿望单，关注最新开发进度，一起打造这个世界的未来吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
